<template>
  <v-card
    class="mx-auto"
    width="400" 
  >
    <template v-slot:title>{{user.username}}</template> 
    <v-card-text>
      {{user.email}} | {{user.age}}
    </v-card-text>
  </v-card>
</template>

<script>

import axios from 'axios';
export default {
    name:'UserDetail',
    props:["user"],
    created(){ 
        
        axios.get('http://localhost:5000/users/'+this.$route.params.id).then(response=>{
            console.log(response.data);
        });
    }
}
</script>
